    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>In the Wild</strong> is an educational game where you play as real forest animals, roam a beautiful island, and collect fact orbs to learn real-world facts about the animals you control.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >         <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575380/extras/adfe8060820deba825d8f87941148105.avif?t=1749108021\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575380/extras_big/adfe8060820deba825d8f87941148105.avif?t=1749108021 width=800 height=446 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Learn Through Exploration</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each animal has its own set of unique facts scattered across the island.  <br>Find them, collect them, and our in-game guide will display the fact and read it aloud to you - teaching you something new with every discovery.  <br> <br>With hundreds of facts scattered across the island, there's plenty to explore and learn.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Original Soundtrack</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the atmosphere of the island with our custom soundtrack, composed by WesWolf Productions to perfectly complement the game's beautiful environment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Dynamic Time &amp; Weather</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Our dynamic time and weather system enables an additional layer of interaction with the world. As a player, you can choose to use real-world time (relative to their time-zone) or our in-game time. <br><br>Want clear skies all the time? You also have the ability to disable weather entirely. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >How you play is completely up to you.   <br><br>Escape into nature and enjoy your time <strong>In the Wild</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >         <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575380/extras/f6a44e48702171fb354e4b2e7cbc1b14.avif?t=1749108021\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575380/extras_big/f6a44e48702171fb354e4b2e7cbc1b14.avif?t=1749108021 width=800 height=448 /></span></p>",
